{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:1",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلنَّٰزِعَٰتِ غَرۡقٗا",
      "translation": "Demi (malaikat) yang mencabut (nyawa) dengan keras.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:2",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلنَّٰشِطَٰتِ نَشۡطٗا",
      "translation": "Demi (malaikat) yang mencabut (nyawa) dengan lemah lembut.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:3",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلسَّٰبِحَٰتِ سَبۡحٗا",
      "translation": "Demi (malaikat) yang turun dari langit dengan cepat,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:4",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَٱلسَّٰبِقَٰتِ سَبۡقٗا",
      "translation": "dan (malaikat) yang mendahului dengan kencang,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:5",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَٱلۡمُدَبِّرَٰتِ أَمۡرٗا",
      "translation": "dan (malaikat) yang mengatur urusan (dunia).895)",
      "footnotes": "*895) Dalam ayat 1-5 Allah bersumpah dengan malaikat-malaikat yang bermacam-macam sifat dan urusannya bahwa manusia akan dibangkitkan pada hari Kiamat. Sebagian mufasir berpendapat, bahwa dalam ayat-ayat ini, kecuali ayat 5, Allah bersumpah dengan bintang-bintang."
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:6",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَوۡمَ تَرۡجُفُ ٱلرَّاجِفَةُ",
      "translation": "(Sungguh, kamu akan dibangkitkan) pada hari ketika tiupan pertama mengguncangkan alam,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:7",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَتۡبَعُهَا ٱلرَّادِفَةُ",
      "translation": "(tiupan pertama) itu diiringi oleh tiupan kedua.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:8",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "قُلُوبٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ وَاجِفَةٌ",
      "translation": "Hati manusia pada waktu itu merasa sangat takut,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:9",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَبۡصَٰرُهَا خَٰشِعَةٞ",
      "translation": "pandangannya tunduk.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:10",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَقُولُونَ أَءِنَّا لَمَرۡدُودُونَ فِي ٱلۡحَافِرَةِ",
      "translation": "(orang-orang kafir) berkata, \"Apakah kita benar-benar akan dikembalikan kepada kehidupan yang semula?896)",
      "footnotes": "*896) Setelah orang-orang kafir mendengar adanya hari kebangkitan setelah mati mereka merasa heran dan mengejek sebab menurut keyakinan mereka tidak ada hari kebangkitan. Itulah sebabnya mereka bertanya."
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:11",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَءِذَا كُنَّا عِظَٰمٗا نَّخِرَةٗ",
      "translation": "Apakah (akan dibangkitkan juga) apabila kita telah menjadi tulang belulang yang hancur?\"",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "verse_number": 12,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:12",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "قَالُواْ تِلۡكَ إِذٗا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٞ",
      "translation": "Mereka berkata, \"Kalau demikian, itu adalah suatu pengembalian yang merugikan.\"",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "verse_number": 13,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:13",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجۡرَةٞ وَٰحِدَةٞ",
      "translation": "Maka pengembalian itu hanyalah dengan sekali tiupan saja.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "verse_number": 14,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:14",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَإِذَا هُم بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ",
      "translation": "Maka seketika itu mereka hidup kembali di bumi (yang baru).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "verse_number": 15,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "79:15",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ مُوسَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "Sudahkah sampai kepadamu (Muhammad) kisah Musa?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "verse_number": 16,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:16",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِذۡ نَادَىٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ بِٱلۡوَادِ ٱلۡمُقَدَّسِ طُوًى",
      "translation": "Ketika Tuhan memanggilnya (Musa) di lembah suci yaitu Lembah Tuwa;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "verse_number": 17,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:17",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ٱذۡهَبۡ إِلَىٰ فِرۡعَوۡنَ إِنَّهُۥ طَغَىٰ",
      "translation": "pergilah engkau kepada Fir'aun! Sesungguhnya dia telah melampaui batas,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "verse_number": 18,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:18",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَقُلۡ هَل لَّكَ إِلَىٰٓ أَن تَزَكَّىٰ",
      "translation": "Maka katakanlah (kepada Fir'aun), \"Adakah keinginanmu untuk membersihkan diri (dari kesesatan),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "verse_number": 19,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:19",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَهۡدِيَكَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَتَخۡشَىٰ",
      "translation": "dan engkau akan kubimbing ke jalan Tuhanmu agar engkau takut kepada-Nya?\"",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "verse_number": 20,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:20",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَأَرَىٰهُ ٱلۡأٓيَةَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ",
      "translation": "Lalu (Musa) memperlihatkan kepadanya mukjizat yang besar.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "verse_number": 21,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:21",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَكَذَّبَ وَعَصَىٰ",
      "translation": "Tetapi dia (Fir'aun) mendustakan dan mendurhakai.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "verse_number": 22,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:22",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ يَسۡعَىٰ",
      "translation": "Kemudian dia berpaling seraya berusaha menantang (Musa).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "verse_number": 23,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:23",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَحَشَرَ فَنَادَىٰ",
      "translation": "Kemudian dia mengumpulkan (pembesar-pembesarnya) lalu berseru (memanggil kaumnya).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "verse_number": 24,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:24",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَقَالَ أَنَا۠ رَبُّكُمُ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ",
      "translation": "(Seraya) berkata, \"Akulah tuhanmu yang paling tinggi.\"",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "verse_number": 25,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:25",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَأَخَذَهُ ٱللَّهُ نَكَالَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "Maka Allah menghukumnya dengan azab di akhirat dan siksaan di dunia.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "verse_number": 26,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:26",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّ فِي ذَٰلِكَ لَعِبۡرَةٗ لِّمَن يَخۡشَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "Sungguh, pada yang demikian itu terdapat pelajaran bagi orang yang takut (kepada Allah).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "verse_number": 27,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:27",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ءَأَنتُمۡ أَشَدُّ خَلۡقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُۚ بَنَىٰهَا",
      "translation": "Apakah penciptaan kamu yang lebih hebat ataukah langit yang telah dibangun-Nya?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "verse_number": 28,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:28",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "رَفَعَ سَمۡكَهَا فَسَوَّىٰهَا",
      "translation": "Dia telah meninggikan bangunannya lalu menyempurnakannya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "verse_number": 29,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:29",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَغۡطَشَ لَيۡلَهَا وَأَخۡرَجَ ضُحَىٰهَا",
      "translation": "dan Dia menjadikan malamnya (gelap gulita), dan menjadikan siangnya (terang benderang).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "verse_number": 30,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:30",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلۡأَرۡضَ بَعۡدَ ذَٰلِكَ دَحَىٰهَآ",
      "translation": "Dan setelah itu bumi Dia hamparkan.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "verse_number": 31,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:31",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَخۡرَجَ مِنۡهَا مَآءَهَا وَمَرۡعَىٰهَا",
      "translation": "Darinya Dia pancarkan mata air, dan (ditumbuhkan) tumbuh-tumbuhannya.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "verse_number": 32,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:32",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَرۡسَىٰهَا",
      "translation": "Dan gunung-gunung Dia pancangkan dengan kokoh.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "verse_number": 33,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:33",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "مَتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ",
      "translation": "(Semua itu) untuk kesenanganmu dan untuk hewan-hewan ternakmu.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "verse_number": 34,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:34",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلطَّآمَّةُ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ",
      "translation": "Maka apabila malapetaka besar (hari Kiamat) telah datang,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "verse_number": 35,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:35",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَوۡمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا سَعَىٰ",
      "translation": "yaitu pada hari (ketika) manusia teringat akan apa yang telah dikerjakannya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "verse_number": 36,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:36",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَبُرِّزَتِ ٱلۡجَحِيمُ لِمَن يَرَىٰ",
      "translation": "dan neraka diperlihatkan dengan jelas kepada setiap orang yang melihat.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "verse_number": 37,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:37",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَأَمَّا مَن طَغَىٰ",
      "translation": "Maka adapun orang yang melampaui batas,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "verse_number": 38,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:38",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَءَاثَرَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا",
      "translation": "dan lebih mengutamakan kehidupan dunia,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "verse_number": 39,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:39",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ",
      "translation": "maka sungguh, nerakalah tempat tinggalnya.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "verse_number": 40,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:40",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَافَ مَقَامَ رَبِّهِۦ وَنَهَى ٱلنَّفۡسَ عَنِ ٱلۡهَوَىٰ",
      "translation": "Dan adapun orang-orang yang takut kepada kebesaran Tuhannya dan menahan diri dari (keinginan) hawa nafsunya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "verse_number": 41,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:41",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَنَّةَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ",
      "translation": "maka sungguh, surgalah tempat tinggal-(nya).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "verse_number": 42,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:42",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَسۡـَٔلُونَكَ عَنِ ٱلسَّاعَةِ أَيَّانَ مُرۡسَىٰهَا",
      "translation": "Mereka (orang-orang kafir) bertanya kepadamu (Muhammad) tentang hari Kiamat, \"Kapankah terjadinya?\"",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "verse_number": 43,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:43",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فِيمَ أَنتَ مِن ذِكۡرَىٰهَآ",
      "translation": "Untuk apa engkau perlu menyebutkannya (waktunya)?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "verse_number": 44,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:44",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ مُنتَهَىٰهَآ",
      "translation": "Kepada Tuhanmulah (dikembalikan) kesudahannya (ketentuan waktunya).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "verse_number": 45,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:45",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُنذِرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰهَا",
      "translation": "Engkau (Muhammad) hanyalah pemberi peringatan bagi siapa yang takut kepadanya (hari Kiamat).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "verse_number": 46,
      "page_number": 584,
      "verse_key": "79:46",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَأَنَّهُمۡ يَوۡمَ يَرَوۡنَهَا لَمۡ يَلۡبَثُوٓاْ إِلَّا عَشِيَّةً أَوۡ ضُحَىٰهَا",
      "translation": "Pada hari ketika mereka melihat hari Kiamat itu (karena suasananya hebat), mereka merasa seakan-akan hanya (sebentar saja) tinggal (di dunia) pada waktu sore atau pagi hari.",
      "footnotes": ""
    }
  ]
}